sulin, particularly in patients with advanced age and/or renal impairment.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/107456/', '', 'Liraglutide, Lixisenatide', 'Felodipine, Amlodipine, Verapamil, Amlodipine, Atorvastatin, Simvastatin, Lovastatin, Rosuvastatin, Pravastatin, Ezetimibe, Bempedoic acid', 1767369485);
